## Rules

- All release notes must be in **Dutch**
- Use clear, user-friendly language (not too technical)
- Group related changes together
- Use the current date as the release date (format: YYYY-MM-DD)
- Include context about what changed and why it matters to users
- For technical changes, explain the user-facing impact if any
- Keep descriptions concise but informative

